Get Robot Review
    Set Selenium Speed    ${wait_speed}
    Click Button    id:preview
    Set Selenium Speed    ${base_speed}
    #Scroll Element Into View    id:robot-preview-image
    #Screenshot.Set Screenshot Directory    ./output/robots
